  methods: {
    async openModal(id) {
      const counter = useCounterStore()
      // counter.increment()
      counter.count = id
      console.log(counter.count)

      const modal = await modalController
        .create({
          component: Modal,
          initialBreakpoint: 0.5,
          breakpoints: [0, 0.5, 1],
          username: "matt"
        })
      // console.log(bla)
      return modal.present();
    },  
    save_id(id) {
      const counter = useCounterStore()
      // counter.increment()
      counter.count = id
      console.log(counter.count)
    }
  }
});
</script>
